PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FA London bus driver says poor working
OL,8,Fconditions are putting safety at risk.
OL,10,FAn investigation by ITV News London
OL,11,Funcovered claims that long hours,
OL,12,Fexhausting schedules and inadequate
OL,13,Frest are leading to widespread fatigue.
OL,15,FSome drivers fear the workload could
OL,16,Feven lead to accidents.
OL,18,FCurrent rules address a number of the
OL,19,Fissues including regulation of driving
OL,20,Fhours, but workers say they don't go
OL,21,Ffar enough.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FIn November 2024, a campaign for a
OL,8,FLondon Bus Workers' Bill of Rights was
OL,9,Fstarted.
OL,11,FIt included better rest time, toilet
OL,12,Ffacilities and appropriate temperature
OL,13,Fcontrol for different seasons.
OL,15,FA petition was also handed into
OL,16,Fparliament asking for the campaign to
OL,17,Fbe made into legislation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FHowever, one current driver who spoke
OL,8,Fto ITV News London anonymously, said
OL,9,Fdrivers "feel ignored" by TFL and
OL,10,Ftheir operators.
OL,12,FThe driver, who we have called Clare
OL,13,FSmith, said: "TFL have chosen to
OL,14,Fignore it and it shows in the
OL,15,Fschedules, you know, with making us
OL,16,Fwork longer shifts when they change
OL,17,Fthe rotors and cutting down our stand
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"...You've got the controllers who are
OL,8,Fencouraging or trying to pressure us
OL,9,Fnot to take toilet breaks, like, go
OL,10,Fout straight away because it helps
OL,11,Ftheir statistics."
OL,13,FBut as well as not taking breaks, a
OL,14,Flack of toilets also poses a problem
OL,15,Ffor many drivers.
OL,17,FAccording to the London Assembly,
OL,18,Fthere are 675 bus routes - but nearly
OL,19,Fa quarter of them do not have these
OL,20,Ffacilities.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FClare says she has had to resort to
OL,8,Fother ways to relieve herself and this
OL,9,Fisn't uncommon.
OL,11,F"I know that a lot of drivers use
OL,12,Fbottles because either the facilities
OL,13,Fprovided are non existent or just
OL,14,Freally disgusting," she said.
OL,16,F"I've used a jar, a newspaper and baby
OL,17,Fwipes... I'm not in the cab, I've gone
OL,18,Fupstairs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"But it isn't uncommon to do that.
OL,8,FIt's just you haven't got the time.
OL,9,FYou don't want to lose the mileage for
OL,10,Fthe company and there aren't any
OL,11,Ffacilities."
OL,13,FOn Thursday 19 March, drivers in East
OL,14,FLondon walked out in a similar dispute
OL,15,Fto the issues raised by Clare.
OL,17,FThe Unite Union say driver fatigue is
OL,18,Fa "very serious problem".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FThey blame long shifts, insufficient
OL,8,Fbreaks and inadequate running times
OL,9,Fthat leads to drivers working overtime.
OL,11,FJohn Murphy, the reginal officer for
OL,12,FUnite, said: "If fatigue really
OL,13,Fmattered, what we wouldn't be doing is
OL,14,Fmaking drivers work excessive hours,
OL,15,Fgoing backwards and forwards on the
OL,16,Fbusiest roads in Europe."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FHe adds: "What we're saying is give us
OL,8,Fsensible schedules that are not
OL,9,Fflogging us to death, that are not
OL,10,Fmaking things dangerous because people
OL,11,Fare suffering from fatigue, and we
OL,12,Falso want to go home and see our
OL,13,Ffamilies now and then so it's about
OL,14,Frespect, it's about dignity as much as
OL,15,Fanything else."
OL,17,FStagecoach, which employs those at
OL,18,Ftoday's walkout, said: "We remain
OL,19,Fcommitted to continuing this dialogue
OL,20,Fto resolve the issues.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"It is important to say that all
OL,8,Fschedules, duties and rotas have been
OL,9,Fcompiled in line with the agreements
OL,10,Fwe have with Unite that have been in
OL,11,Fplace for many years, and which are
OL,12,Fdesigned to ensure safety of operation.
OL,14,F"While there have been changes
OL,15,Ffollowing amendments by TfL to some
OL,16,Froutes, these all remain within
OL,17,Fagreements and there has been no
OL,18,Fmaterial changes to the average times
OL,19,Fon duty."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FClare adds that overtime is very
OL,8,Fcommon especially with all the
OL,9,Fdifferent employment contracts and as
OL,10,Fthe cost of living goes up.
OL,12,F"I'm not on such a great contract,"
OL,13,Fshe explains.
OL,15,F"The senior drivers have been on
OL,16,Fcontracts that have more benefits and
OL,17,Fthen they cut the benefits in the
OL,18,Flater contracts.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"So the drivers that have been there
OL,8,Ffor one to about four, five years - it
OL,9,Fgoes up a bit every year - they have
OL,10,Fto maybe work more shifts to make ends
OL,11,Fmeet because it's not cheap to live in
OL,12,FLondon. "
OL,14,FThese concerns aren't new either.
OL,16,FA London Assembly Transport Committee
OL,17,Freport commissioned in 2017 found
OL,18,Fdriver fatigue was a chronic issue and
OL,19,Furged TfL to make improvements.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FA report in 2019 by TfL also found
OL,8,Fthat 17% of drivers had fallen asleep
OL,9,Fat the wheel.
OL,11,FKevin Mustafa, a former bus driver,
OL,12,Fquit his job after five years because
OL,13,Fof the working conditions.
OL,15,FHe explained how fatigue caused him to
OL,16,Ffall asleep at the wheel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"Luckily enough I was stationary - but
OL,8,Fsome of these incidents that are
OL,9,Fhappening on the road - absolutely
OL,10,Fsome of those, in my opinion tie back
OL,11,Fto fatigue on London's buses," he said.
OL,13,F"It kind of got pushed to one side and
OL,14,Fforgotten about and the industry's
OL,15,Fcontinued going forward and there's
OL,16,Fbus routes which are being cut so some
OL,17,Fdrivers are getting pushed to the
OL,18,Flimit.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"There's a shortage of drivers because
OL,8,Fdrivers are walking away from the job
OL,9,Fbecause it's becoming unbearable."
OL,11,FBut Clare adds the fatigue is
OL,12,Fexacerbated by scheduling issues.
OL,14,F"So if you're working seven days and
OL,15,Fyou're doing 10 hour shifts, that's 70
OL,16,Fhours you're doing because they
OL,17,Fscheduled it that way. You don't have
OL,18,Fa choice," she said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"...How can you keep people safe? When
OL,8,Fyou get to your seventh day, you're so
OL,9,Fmentally tired because you are looking
OL,10,Fout for hazards every few seconds
OL,11,Fbecause people do very dangerous
OL,12,Fthings around the bus all the time."
OL,14,FLike Kevin, she has also been impacted
OL,15,Fby tiredness whilst working.
OL,17,F"I've been very too tired to drive. I
OL,18,Fthink we all have," she said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"We do the best we can with sleep but
OL,8,Fsometimes the time they give you
OL,9,Fbetween shifts - it's not adequate."
OL,11,FClare believes that this could be
OL,12,Fcontributing to road accidents.
OL,14,FThere were four in February alone -
OL,15,Fthough the reason for these is still
OL,16,Funder investigation and TFL say they
OL,17,Fare "dedicated" to learning from every
OL,18,Fincident and they have made "strong
OL,19,Fprogress" on bus safety.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FWhen asked about why these crashes
OL,8,Fcould be happening, Claire said: "I
OL,9,Fthink it's more likely to be driver
OL,10,Ffatigue than anything else because I
OL,11,Fthink sometimes they are experienced
OL,12,Fdrivers, they must be tired because
OL,13,Fyou don't make those sort of mistakes
OL,14,Fknowing the stakes.
OL,16,F"I mean, just because profit comes
OL,17,Fbefore anything else, then they will
OL,18,Frush people through. So maybe some of
OL,19,Fthem are new drivers too."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G17/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FAnother former bus driver, Lorraine
OL,8,FRobertson says she was in a constant
OL,9,Floop of fatigue and worry during her
OL,10,F20 years of service.J"Am I going to
OL,11,Fcrash?" she said,
OL,13,F"That is my worst fear that I would
OL,14,Factually crash my bus and hurt people.
OL,15,FIt's just stressful.
OL,17,F"The feeling of being dehydrated
OL,18,Fshakes, headaches, disorientated, i
OL,19,Fthink that always put me on edge every
OL,20,Ftime I got on the bus I'm thinking
OL,21,Fwhere am I going to use the toilet."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G18/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FTfL said: "Bus drivers play an
OL,8,Fessential role in keeping the capital
OL,9,Fmoving. Alongside bus operators, TfL
OL,10,Ftakes their safety and welfare
OL,11,Fseriously and TfL rightly requires
OL,12,Foperators to meet high standards
OL,14,F"TfL is working together with
OL,15,Foperators on a range of measures to
OL,16,Ffurther improve working conditions,
OL,17,Fhealth and wellbeing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G19/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774026671
OL,3,CAsleep at the wheel and urinating in
OL,4,Cjars - the reality for London's bus
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"TfL is committed to ensuring that all
OL,8,Fstaff have a fair work schedule, with
OL,9,Fsafe vehicles and access to the
OL,10,Ffacilities they need to carry out
OL,11,Ftheir roles effectively."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G20/20
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
